@startuml cancelEvent
title Cancel Event
actor Admin
Admin -> System: deleteEvent(eventId)
System -> Server: handleEvents(HttpExchange exchange)
Server -> Database: deleteEvent(Event event)
Database --> Server: success
Server -> NotificationService: sendCancellationMessage (recipient, message)\n(for affected users)
NotificationService --> Server: sent
Server --> System: success
System --> Admin: Event cancelled and users notified
@enduml